---
title: Smart Zesty Chicken Meatballs with Lemon-Garlic Sauce and Mini Wedges
description: Lemon zest gives these chicken meatballs brightness and provides a nice counterpoint to the garlic sauce. The creamy dill dressing on the salad gives off Mediterranean vibes and the mini potato wedges are just adorable.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-poulet-citronnees-8800728f.jpg
